1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:01,860
You've survived worse.

2
00:00:04,220 --> 00:00:07,160
This isn't about your pathetic little cut.

3
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:09,680
It's about that girl you killed.

4
00:00:12,066 --> 00:00:15,026
We've never killed a human before,
have we?

5
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:17,920
Sure, mountains of robot corpses.

6
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:22,260
This... this was the first human being.

7
00:00:22,940 --> 00:00:25,140
Real flesh and blood.

8
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:28,440
What happens when the others find you?

9
00:00:28,441 --> 00:00:31,100
You'll have to kill them too, can you?

10
00:00:32,159 --> 00:00:35,120
Will you be able to when the time comes?

11
00:00:35,460 --> 00:00:37,280
Maybe they will kill you?

12
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,700
Or is that what you want?

